{"tid":48732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(又可以炒口罩)內地霧霾閉天　明日殺到本港？","createTime":"2016-12-21T08:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T16:18:51.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"424ac3d00cd7a413cb96b2ea5c1294320a1dd7f9","tid":48732,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/熱話/61244/內地霧霾閉天-明日殺到本港-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F61244%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%A7%E9%9C%BE%E9%96%89%E5%A4%A9-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E6%AE%BA%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF-&d=NztypxuZbm0QUhDvt%2FI623vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=3545491c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/熱話/61244/內地霧霾閉天-明日殺到本港-</a><br />\n<br />\n內地連日受到嚴重的霧霾天氣影響，內地大面積被霧霾覆蓋，中央氣象台自上周五發布最高級別的霧霾紅色警報後，星期二、三進入高峰期，華北和東北等11個省市，相當於中國大陸六分一土地會出現重度霧霾，最低能見度不到500米，部分地區 PM2.5 濃度每立方米超過500微克。<br />\n<br />\nNHK報道，東京大學「SPRINTARS」系統預測，霧霾天氣將會殺到香港，PM2.5污染物會在今日開始向南移動，明日橫越本港，到聖誕節過後才稍有改善。"},{"pid":"012936e68047d921da6f2a3ca759d50cdc70e083","tid":48732,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:55:23.000Z","msg":"港豬又有野炒la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d09ded47f315954e76ea14077a1a9e26c400d4d","tid":48732,"uid":37736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:59:51.000Z","msg":"沙士用剩嘅n95 有冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e8babe74c346249feef60afbce027e0db7b466","tid":48732,"uid":22919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沙士用剩嘅n95 有冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 13年前既"},{"pid":"2ffd31bcf4677d7ccccfa76c57dd4d21bd86ed06","tid":48732,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockqu